<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="U" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Unhacked" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Unhacked,</orth> not hacked, not blunted by blows: <cit><quote>with u. swords and helmets all unbruised,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 2.254" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 254</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to part with u. edges,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 2.6.38" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 6, 38</bibl></cit>.
